OL,3,CTrump's tariffs force one of China's
OL,4,Cindustrial hubs to a standstill
OL,6,FITV News Asia correspondent Debi
OL,7,FEdward reports from Dongguan - a
OL,8,Fmanufacturing center where exports to
OL,9,Fthe United States make up nearly 70%
OL,10,Fof their output
OL,12,FIt is in places like Dongguan in
OL,13,Fsouthern China where Donald Trump's
OL,14,Ftariffs are hitting the hardest.
OL,16,FThe city is a hub for tech and
OL,17,Findustrial manufacturing, and it is
OL,18,Fone of many cities in Guangdong
OL,19,Fprovince which helped build and
OL,20,Fmaintain China's reputation as the
OL,21,Ffactory of the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
