OL,3,CTrump's tariffs force one of China's
OL,4,Cindustrial hubs to a standstill
OL,6,FOne of the things that strikes you
OL,7,Fmost when you visit the industrial
OL,8,Fheartlands of China, is not just the
OL,9,Fsheer number of factories dedicated to
OL,10,Fthe country's export industry, it's
OL,11,Fthe scale of the workforce required to
OL,12,Fsupport it.
OL,14,FNext to, or even within most of the
OL,15,Fproduction sites in Dongguan, there
OL,16,Fare huge dormitories to house the
OL,17,Fthousands of workers making
OL,18,Felectronics, plastics and machinery
OL,19,Ffor the rest of the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
