OL,3,CTrump's tariffs force one of China's
OL,4,Cindustrial hubs to a standstill
OL,6,FIn the short term it is hard to see
OL,7,Fanywhere replicating the output of
OL,8,FChina - and not just in terms of the
OL,9,Fsize, in terms of skill and supply
OL,10,Fchains too.
OL,12,FWe visited a toymaker in neighbouring
OL,13,FShenzhen and the owner, Hong Binbin
OL,14,Ftold us that from receiving an order
OL,15,Ffrom a client, it can be made and
OL,16,Fshipped to them, in bulk, in sixty
OL,17,Fdays.
OL,19,FHe said the same process would take
OL,20,Fsix months in Vietnam, a country
OL,21,Femerging as a manufacturing powerhouse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
