OL,3,CTrump's tariffs force one of China's
OL,4,Cindustrial hubs to a standstill
OL,6,FApril should be one of the busiest
OL,7,Ftimes for Hong Binbin's factory but
OL,8,Fwhen he took us to the factory floor,
OL,9,Fmost of the sewing machine stations
OL,10,Fwere sitting empty.
OL,12,FHe told us that due to the tariffs,
OL,13,Forders have dried up and he's had to
OL,14,Fput workers on forced leave.
