OL,4,Cindustrial hubs to a standstill
OL,6,FThis is usually when they begin work
OL,7,Fmaking and boxing up deliveries for
OL,8,FChristmas, but their main market is
OL,9,Fthe United States, and customers have
OL,10,Fbeen calling to cancel orders, and
OL,11,Fstopped placing new ones.
OL,13,FHe showed us a pile of boxes that were
OL,14,Fdue to get shipped to California, but
OL,15,Fthey are sitting in his warehouse
OL,16,Fwhile the client waits to see what
OL,17,Fhappens with the tariffs. After the
OL,18,Flatest round of tariffs, toys are
OL,19,Fbeing taxed at 145%.
