OL,3,CTrump's tariffs force one of China's
OL,4,Cindustrial hubs to a standstill
OL,6,FIn Dongguan, we ran into a group of
OL,7,Fyoung men standing beside a job
OL,8,Fadvertisement board outside one of the
OL,9,Felectronics factories.
OL,11,FThey'd come to southern China having
OL,12,Fbeen told that the number of factories
OL,13,Fin the region would guarantee them
OL,14,Fsome work. It hasn't quite worked out.
OL,16,FThey've been searching for days but
OL,17,Ffinding that either companies are not
OL,18,Fhiring, or only with reduced hours and
OL,19,Fsalaries. Youth unemployment has been
OL,20,Fhigh since the pandemic, and now the
OL,21,Ftariffs have made things worse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
