OL,6,FThe Chinese government continues to
OL,7,Fpaint a robust and somewhat optimistic
OL,8,Feconomic outlook. Figures published
OL,9,Ffor January to March show the economy
OL,10,Fgrew 5.4% year on year - a rate double
OL,11,Fthat of the United States.
OL,13,FA spokesman for the national
OL,14,Fstatistics bureau described the
OL,15,FChinese economy as stable with a
OL,16,Frobust spirit and big potential.
