OL,3,CTrump's tariffs force one of China's
OL,4,Cindustrial hubs to a standstill
OL,6,FHe said the country is capable and
OL,7,Fconfident it can handle external
OL,8,Fchallenges and achieve its growth
OL,9,Ftarget - but those positive growth
OL,10,Ffigures represent the months before
OL,11,FDonald Trump raised tariffs on Chinese
OL,12,Fexports. Some sectors now being taxed
OL,13,Fup to 245%.
OL,15,FThe world's two largest economies are
OL,16,Flocked in a trade war of attrition -
OL,17,Fand the pain for workers in China is
OL,18,Fonly just starting to pile on.
